    COORD --> DI
    DI --> FE
    FE --> AT
    AT --> MS
    MS --> IN
    
    %% Data Storage
    FE --> CACHE
    MS --> CACHE
    IN --> CACHE
    CONFIG --> COORD
    
    %% Dashboard Data Flow
    CACHE --> DASH
    COORD --> DASH
    
